#Celsius to Fahrenheit Temperature Converter
#Write a program that converts Celcius temperatures to Fahrenheit.
#Formula: F=95C+32
#The program should ask the user for a temperature in celsius and display the
#results in Fahrenheit

celsius = float(input("Celsius: > "))

conversion_F = format(((celsius * 1.8) + 32),'.2f')

print("Temperature in Fahrenheit: ", conversion_F)
